{"tid":524497,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潘樂陶公司投得高鐵工程","createTime":"2018-01-09T15:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T17:14:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef3ef40324b8c15a59ee5e3d23305a67e3c7e92","tid":524497,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180109/20269118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F20269118&d=L8MSUQG7MI8HI5HnTx905wKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=3615a71a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F20269118&h=22ff8950\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180109/20269118</a><br />\n<br />\n潘樂陶公司投得高鐵工程<br />\n<br />\n37,774<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180109/large/1515430141_3d2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180109%2Flarge%2F1515430141_3d2b.jpg&h=da2446da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■潘樂陶（左二）昨現身法律年活動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】律政司司長鄭若驊丈夫兼鄰居、工程師學會前會長潘樂陶在其創辦的安樂工程集團出任主席。《蘋果》翻查安樂工程集團通訊發現，該公司於2011年投得兩項高鐵工程合約，包括隧道通風樓及緊急救援處屋宇設備，以及石崗列車停放處屋宇設備，合約總值逾4.38億元。<br />\n據安樂工程集團2011年集團通訊《樂訊》顯示，該公司取得港鐵公司工程合約，成為三項大型工程承包商，包括高鐵隧道通風樓及緊急救援處屋宇設備（高鐵合約編號：855）、石崗列車停放處屋宇設備（高鐵合約編號：856），及西港島綫軌旁設備及隧道環境控制系統（西港島綫合約編號753）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5年接8億元政府工程<br />\n<br />\n《樂訊》更指出，安樂工程集團需為兩個高鐵工程有關屋宇設施，包括環境控制系統、電力、消防系統，及樓宇自控系統等，提供全面的設計、供應及安裝等服務，兩個高鐵工程項目預計2015年完工。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有傳媒報道，潘樂陶名下公司於過去5年，在香港承接的政府工程合約至少有24份，總工程款額達8.17億元，當中包括入境處自助過關「e-道」系統、渠務署「淨化海港計劃」等。<br />\n<br />\n■記者譚靜雯、鍾雅宜  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n鄭若驊前年再婚　梁愛詩主持婚禮<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n涉貪案提訊　何志平否認控罪　官拒保釋"},{"pid":"a37176bbe8c38cb5d20be6a2f3421d8058acb8e6","tid":524497,"uid":110339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"06a567e42e102936a5aadc23e42bbd19de231bd4","tid":524497,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1a7f7f00fd2ac834e15aeeac441fe81fa8739b","tid":524497,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>律政司司長鄭若驊<span style=\"color: red;\">丈夫兼鄰居</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafbc1ae74e02a7ae4718da2237c93f94e393001","tid":524497,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}